Module com.example.demo
Package com.example.demo.Level1

Class LevelOneConfig

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.Level1.LevelOneConfig
public class LevelOneConfig extends Object
Configuration class for Level 1 of the game. This class contains constants related to the game level's background, enemies, player configuration, and UI settings. The class is designed to prevent instantiation by throwing an AssertionError in its private constructor.
